  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <lg xml:id="TolC080">
          <l>iyaṟkaiyiṉuṭaimaiyiṉ muṟaimaiyiṟkiḻamaiyiṟ</l>
	<l>ceyaṟkaiyiṉ mutumaiyiṉ viṉaiyi ṉeṉṟā</l>
	<l>karuviyiṟ ṟuṇaiyiṟ kalattiṉ mutali</l> 
	<l>ṉoruvaḻi yuṟuppiṟ kuḻuvi ṉeṉṟā</l>
	<l>terintumoḻicceytiyi ṉilaiyiṉvāḻcciyiṟ</l>
	<l>ṟirintuvēṟu paṭūum piṟavu maṉṉa</l>
	<l>kūṟiya maruṅkiṟ ṟōṉṟuṅ kiḷavi</l>
	<l>yāṟaṉ pāla veṉmaṉār pulavar.</l>
        </lg>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/62/mode/1up">62</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/64/mode/1up">64</ref>.</p>
      <p>ic cūttiram eṉṉutaliṟṟō veṉiṉ, muṟaiyāṉē āṟām vēṟṟumai uṇarttutal nutaliṟṟu.</p>
      <p>urai: āṟām eṇṇumuṟaimaikkaṇṇatu atu eṉṉum peyaraiyuṭaiya vēṟṟumaiccol; taṉṉoṭu toṭarntatōr poruḷaiyum taṉṉiṉ vēṟāyatōr poruḷaiyum itaṉatitu eṉṟu kiḻamai ceppiniṟṟal āṟām vēṟṟumaiyatu ilakkaṇam eṉṟavāṟu.</p>
      <p>atuvē eṉpatu apporuḷai virippāṉ terittavāṟu.</p>
      <p>‘itaṉatu itu’ eṉṉuṅ kiḷavikkiḻamaittu eṉṉātu, ‘aṉṉa’ eṉṟataṉāṉ, itaṟkup piṟitumoru poruḷ uṇṭu eṉka. aḵtiyātō veṉiṉ, avaṉa avaḷa eṉṉum īṟṟakaram. taṉṉiṉum eṉpuḻit taṟkiḻamai aintu vakaippaṭum, oṉṟu palakuḻīiya taṟkiḻamaiyum, vēṟu pala kuḻīiya taṟkiḻamaiyum, oṉṟiyaṟ kiḻamaiyum, uṟuppiṉ kiḻamaiyum, meytirintāya kiḻamaiyum eṉa.</p>
      <p>oṉṟu palakuḻīiya taṟkiḻamaiyatu:</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Ilam-cit1">
        <l>‘eṭ kuppai’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>eṉpatu.</p>
      <p>vēṟu palakuḻīiya taṟkiḻamaiyatu:</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Ilam-cit2">
        <l>‘paṭaiyatu kuḻām’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>eṉpatu.</p>
      <p>oṉṟiyaṟ kiḻamaiyatu:</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Ilam-cit3">
        <l>‘nilattiṉatu akalam’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>eṉpatu.</p>
      <p>uṟuppiṉ kiḻamaiyatu:</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Ilam-cit4">
        <l>‘yāṉaiyatu kōṭu’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>eṉpatu.</p>
      <p>meytirintākiya kiḻamaiyatu:</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Ilam-cit5">
        <l>‘eḷḷiṉatu cāntu’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>eṉpatu.</p>
      <p>piṟitiṉ kiḻamai itu pōlap pakutippaṭātu.</p>
      <p>iṉi, avviraṇṭu kiḻamaiyum oṭṭumāṟu kāṭṭutum.</p>
      <p>iyaṟkai:</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Ilam-cit6">
        <l>‘cāttaṉa tiyaṟkai’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>eṉpatu.</p>
      <p>uṭaimai:</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Ilam-cit7">
        <l>‘cāttaṉa tuṭaimai’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>eṉpatu.</p>
      <p>muṟaimai:</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Ilam-cit8">
        <l>‘āviṉatu kaṉṟu’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>eṉpatu.</p>
      <p>kiḻamai:</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Ilam-cit9">
        <l>‘cāttaṉatu kiḻamai’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>eṉpatu.</p>
      <p>ceyaṟkai:</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Ilam-cit10">
        <l>‘cāttaṉatu ceyaṟkai’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>eṉpatu.</p>
      <p>mutumai:</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Ilam-cit11">
        <l>‘avaṉatu mutumai’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>eṉpatu.</p>
      <p>viṉai:</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Ilam-cit12">
        <l>‘avaṉatu viṉai’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>eṉpatu.</p>
      <p>karuvi:</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Ilam-cit13">
        <l>‘cāttaṉatu vāḷ’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>eṉpatu.</p>
      <p>tuṇai:</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Ilam-cit14">
        <l>‘avaṉatu tuṇai’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>eṉpatu.</p>
      <p>kalam:</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Ilam-cit15">
        <l>‘cāttaṉatu kalam’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>eṉpatu.</p>
      <p>kalam eṉpatu oṟṟik kalattai.</p>
      <p>mutal:</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Ilam-cit16">
        <l>‘cāttaṉatu mutal’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>eṉpatu.</p>
      <p>oruvaḻi yuṟuppu:</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Ilam-cit17">
        <l>‘yāṉaiyatu kōṭu’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>eṉpatu.</p>
      <p>kuḻūu:</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Ilam-cit18">
        <l>‘paṭaiyatu kuḻūu’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>eṉpatu.</p>
      <p>terintumoḻicceyti:</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Ilam-cit19">
      <l>‘kapilaratu pāṭṭu’</l>
    </lg>
      <p>eṉpatu.</p>
      <p>nilai:</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Ilam-cit20">
      <l>‘cāttaṉatu nilai’</l>
    </lg>
      <p>eṉpatu.</p>
      <p>vāḻcci:</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Ilam-cit21">
      <l>‘cāttaṉatu vāḻcci’</l>
    </lg>
      <p>eṉpatu.</p>
      <p>tirintu vēṟupaṭṭatu:</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Ilam-cit22">
      <l>‘eḷḷiṉatu cāntu’</l>
    </lg>
      <p>eṉpatu.</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Ilam-cit23">
      <l>‘cāttaṉatu col’</l>
    </lg>
      <p>eṉpatum atu.</p>
      <p>piṟavum eṉpatu puṟaṉaṭai.</p>
      <p>kūṟiya maruṅkiṟ ṟōṉṟum kiḷavi āṟaṉpāla eṉpatu irukiḻamaiyumpaṟṟi varuvaṉavum piṟavum ataṉpāla eṉṟavāṟu.  (14)</p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Cēṉāvaraiyar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Ci. Vai. Tamōtarampiḷḷai</persName> 1868, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n85/mode/1up">82</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n87/mode/1up">84</ref>.</p>
      <p>i - ḷ. iyaṟkai mutalāka vāḻcciyīṟākac collappaṭṭaṉavum tirintu vēṟupaṭūumaṉṉapiṟavumākiya mēṟkūṟappaṭṭa kiḻamaipporuṭkaṭ ṭōṉṟuñ collellām āṟāmvēṟṟumaittiṟattaṉaveṉṟu colluvar pulavar. e-ṟu.</p>
<p>tirintu vēṟupaṭūumaṉṉapiṟavumeṉṟārēṉum, tirintu vēṟupaṭutal aṉṉapiṟavumeṉṟataṉāṟṟaḻuvappaṭuvaṉavaṟṟuḷ orucāraṉavaṟṟiṟkē koḷka.</p>
<p>u - m.</p>
<lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit"> 
  eḷḷatu kuppai; 
    </lg>
  <p>paṭaiyatu kuḻām eṉpaṉa kuḻūukkiḻamai. avai muṟaiyāṉē oṉṟu pala kuḻīiyatum vēṟu pala kuḻīiyatumām.</p>
  <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit1">
    cāttaṉatiyaṟkai;
  </lg>
<lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit">
  nilattatakalam 
</lg>
  <p>eṉpaṉa iyaṟkaikkiḻamai.</p>
    <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit2">
    cāttaṉatu nilaimai;
    </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit1">
      cāttaṉatillāmai
      </lg>
      <p>eṉpaṉa nilaikkiḻamai. ivaiyoṉṟiyaṟkiḻamai.</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit3">
      yāṉaiyatu kōṭu;
      </lg>
      <p>puliyatukir eṉpaṉa uṟuppiṉkiḻamai. uṟuppāvatu poruḷiṉēkatēcameṉpataṟivittaṟku oruvaḻiyuṟuppeṉṟār.</p> 
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit4">
      cāttaṉatu ceyaṟkai;
      </lg>
      <p>cāttaṉatu kaṟṟaṟivu eṉpaṉa ceyaṟkaikkiḻamai.</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit5">
      aracaṉatu mutumai;
      </lg>
      <p>aracaṉatu mutirvu eṉpaṉa mutumaikkiḻamai. mutumaiyeṉpatu piṟitorkāraṇam paṟṟātu kālam paṟṟi orutalaiyāka apporuṭkaṭṭōṉṟum paruvamākaliṟ ceyaṟkaiyuḷaṭakkātu vēṟu kūṟiṉār.</p> 
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit6">
      cāttaṉatu toḻil;
      </lg>
      <p>cāttaṉatu celavu eṉpaṉa viṉaikkiḻamai. ivai meytirintāya taṟkiḻamai.</p>
     <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit7"> 
     cāttaṉatuṭaimai;
     </lg>
     <p>cāttaṉatu tōṭṭam eṉpaṉa uṭaimaikkiḻamai.</p> 
     <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit8">
     maṟiyatu tāy;
     </lg>
     <p>maṟiyatu tantai eṉpaṉa muṟaimaikkiḻamai.</p> 
     <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit9">
     icaiyatu karuvi;
     </lg>
     <p>vaṉaikalattatu tikiri eṉpaṉa karuvikkiḻamai.</p> 
     <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit10">
     avaṉatu tuṇai;
     </lg>
     <p>avaṉatiṇaṅku eṉpaṉa tuṇaikkiḻamai.</p>
     <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit11"> 
  nilattatoṟṟikkalam;
  </lg>
  <p>cāttaṉatu vilaittīṭṭu eṉpaṉa kalakkiḻamai.</p> 
    <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit12">
    oṟṟiyatu mutal;
    </lg>
    <p>oṟṟiyatu poruḷ eṉpaṉa mutaṟkiḻamai.</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit13">
      kapilaratu pāṭṭu; 
      </lg>
      <p>paraṇaratu pāṭṭiyal eṉpaṉa ceyyuṭkiḻamai. terintu moḻiyāṟceyyappaṭutaliṟ ṟerintumoḻicceytiyāyiṉa. ivai poruṭpiṟitiṉkiḻamai.</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit14">
      murukaṉatu kuṟiñcinilam;
      </lg>
      <p>veḷḷiyatāṭci eṉpaṉa kiḻamaikkiḻamai.</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit15">
      kāṭṭatiyāṉai;
      </lg>
      <p>yāṉaiyatu kāṭu eṉpaṉa vāḻccikkiḻamai.</p> 
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit16">
      avaṟṟuṇ murukaṉatu kuṟiñcinilam;
      </lg>
      <p>yāṉaiyatu kāṭu eṉpaṉa nilappiṟitiṉkiḻamai. kāṭṭatiyāṉai eṉpatu poruṭpiṟitiṉkiḻamai. ēṉaiyatu kālappiṟitiṉkiḻamai.</p>
<p>tirintu vēṟupaṭūum</p>
  <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit17">
  aṉṉapiṟavum
  </lg>
  <p>eṉṟataṉāl,</p>
  <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit18">
  eṭcāntu; 
  </lg>
  <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit19">
  kōṭṭu nūṟu; 
  </lg>
  <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit20">
  cāttaṉatoppu; 
  </lg>
  <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit21">
  tokaiyatu viri; 
  </lg>
  <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit22">
  poruḷatu kēṭu; 
  </lg>
  <lg xml:id="TolC080-Cena-cit23">
  collatu poruḷ 
  </lg>
  <p>eṉṉuntoṭakkattaṉa koḷka. avaṟṟuḷ eṭcāntu; kōṭṭatu nūṟu eṉpaṉa mutalāyiṉa muḻuvatūuntiritaliṉ, vēṟu kūṟiṉār.</p>
<p>mēṟcollappaṭṭa taṟkiḻamai piṟitiṉkiḻamaiyeṉpaṉavaṟṟai virittavāṟu.	(19)</p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Nacciṉārkkiṉiyar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Irāma. Kōvintacāmipiḷḷai</persName> 1997, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/n126/mode/1up">98</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/n127/mode/1up">99</ref>.</p>
      <p>itu, ataṉai muṭikka varum poruḷ vēṟupāṭu kūṟukiṉṟatu.</p>
      <p>(i-ḷ) iyaṟkai............vāḻcciyiṉ ― iyaṟkkai mutalāka vāḻcci yīṟākac collap paṭṭaṉavum, tirintu vēṟu paṭūu maṉṉa piṟavum ― orucāraṉa tirintu vēṟupaṭu mavai pōlavaṉa piṟavumākiya, kūṟiya maruṅkiṟ ṟōṉṟuṅ kiḷavi - muṟkūṟiya kiḻamaip poruṭkaṭ ṭōṉṟuñ collellām, āṟaṉ pāla veṉmaṉār pulavar - āṟām vēṟṟumait tiṟattaṉa veṉṟu kūṟuvar pulavareṉṟa vāṟu.</p>
      <p>(u-m)</p>
        <lg xml:id="TolC080-Nacc-cit1">
        <l><note xml:lang="en">1</note> eṇṇatu kuppai ―</l>
        </lg>
        <p>iḵtu, oṉṟupala kuḻī iyataṟ kiḻamai.</p>
        <lg xml:id="TolC080-Nacc-cit2">
        <l><note xml:lang="en">3</note> paṭaiyatu kuḻām ―</l>
        </lg>
        <p>itu vēṟu pala kuḻī iyataṟ kiḻamai.</p>
        <lg xml:id="TolC080-Nacc-cit3">
          <l>cāttaṉa tiyaṟkai.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg xml:id="TolC080-Nacc-cit4">
          <l>nilattu akalam ―</l>
        </lg>
        <p>ivai yiyaṟkaik kiḻamai.</p>
        <lg xml:id="TolC080-Nacc-cit5">
          <l>cāttaṉatu nilaimai</l>
        </lg>
        <lg xml:id="TolC080-Nacc-cit6">
          <l>cāttaṉa tillāmai</l>
        </lg>
        <p>ivai nilaikkiḻamai</p>
        <p>innāṉku moṉṟiyaṟ kiḻamai.</p>
      <p>uṟuppāvatu, oruporuḷi ṉēkatēca meṉpa taṟivittaṟ koruvaḻi yuṟuppeṉṟār. avai,</p>
        <lg xml:id="TolC080-Nacc-cit7">
          <l>yāṉaiyatu kōṭu</l>
        </lg>
        <lg xml:id="TolC080-Nacc-cit8">
          <l>puliyatukir</l>
        </lg>
        <p>ivai yuṟuppiṉ kiḻamai</p>
        <p>ceyaṟkaiyāvatu taṉṟaṉmai tirintu vēṟōr taṉmaiyātal avai</p>
        <lg xml:id="TolC080-Nacc-cit9">
          <l>cāttaṉatu ceyaṟkai.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg xml:id="TolC080-Nacc-cit10">
          <l>cāttaṉatu kaṟṟaṟivu.</l>
        </lg>
        <p>mutumaik kiḻamai.</p>
        <lg xml:id="TolC080-Nacc-cit11">
          <l>aracaṉatu mutumai.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg xml:id="TolC080-Nacc-cit12">
          <l>aracaṉatu mutirvu.</l>
        </lg>
        <p>itu, aṟiviṉ mutircci yeṉpa taṟivittaṟ kiḷamai kūṟāyiṉār.</p>
        <p>viṉaikkiḻamai.</p>
        <lg xml:id="TolC080-Nacc-cit13">
          <l>cāttaṉatu viṉai.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg xml:id="TolC080-Nacc-cit14">
          <l>cāttaṉatu celavu.</l>
        </lg>
        <p>ivai meytirintāya taṟkiḻamai.</p>
        <p>uṭaimaik kiḻamai,</p>
        <lg xml:id="TolC080-Nacc-cit15">
          <l>cāttaṉa tuṭaimai</l>
        </lg>
        <lg xml:id="TolC080-Nacc-cit16">
          <l>cāttaṉatu tōṭṭam</l>
        </lg>
        <p>muṟaimaik kiḻamai</p>
        <lg xml:id="TolC080-Nacc-cit17">
          <l>maṟiyatu tāy</l>
        </lg>
        <lg xml:id="TolC080-Nacc-cit18">
          <l>maṟiyatu tantai</l>
        </lg>
        <p>karuvik kiḻamai,</p>
        <lg xml:id="TolC080-Nacc-cit19">
          <l>icaiyatu karuvi</l>
        </lg>
        <lg xml:id="TolC080-Nacc-cit20">
          <l>viṉaikkālattatu tikiri</l>
        </lg>
        <p>tuṇaikkiḻamai,</p>
        <lg xml:id="TolC080-Nacc-cit21">
          <l>avaṉatu tuṇai</l>
        </lg>
        <lg xml:id="TolC080-Nacc-cit22">
          <l>avaṉa tiṇaṅku</l>
        </lg>
        <p>kālamāva tōlai.</p>
        <lg xml:id="TolC080-Nacc-cit23">
          <l>nilatta toṟṟik kalam</l>
        </lg>
        <lg xml:id="TolC080-Nacc-cit24">
          <l>cāttaṉatu vilait tīṭṭu.</l>
        </lg>
        <p>iḵtu iru poruṭkurimai yuṭaimaiyiṉ, uṭaimaiyiṉ vēṟāyiṟṟu.</p>
        <p>mutaṟ kiḻamai,</p>
        <lg xml:id="TolC080-Nacc-cit25">
          <l>oṟṟiyatu mutal</l>
        </lg>
        <lg xml:id="TolC080-Nacc-cit26">
          <l>oṟṟiyatu poruḷ</l>
        </lg>
        <p>terintu moḻicceyti terintu moḻiyāṉ ceyyappaṭutaliṟ ṟerintu moḻic ceytiyāyiṟṟu.</p>
        <lg xml:id="TolC080-Nacc-cit27">
          <l>kapilaratu pāṭṭu</l>
        </lg>
        <p>itu ‘pāriyatu pāṭṭueṉa’ niṟṟali ṉiruporuṭ kuriyatām</p>
        <lg xml:id="TolC080-Nacc-cit28">
        <l>paraṇaratu pāṭṭiyal</l>
        </lg>
        <p>ituvumatu. ivaiporuṭ piṟitiṉ kiḻamai</p>
        <p>kiḻamaikkiḻamai</p>
        <lg xml:id="TolC080-Nacc-cit29">
          <l>murukaṉatu kuṟiñcinilam</l>
        </lg>
        <p>itu nilappiṟitiṉ kiḻamai</p>
        <lg xml:id="TolC080-Nacc-cit30">
          <l>veḷḷiyatu āṭci</l>
        </lg>
        <p>itu kālap piṟitiṉ kiḻamai</p>
        <p>vāḻcci</p>
        <lg xml:id="TolC080-Nacc-cit31">
          <l>kāṭṭatu yāṉai</l>
        </lg>
        <p>itu poruṭpiṟitiṉ kiḻamai</p>
        <lg xml:id="TolC080-Nacc-cit32">
          <l>yāṉaiyatu kāṭu</l>
        </lg>
        <p>itu nilappiṟitiṉ kiḻamai</p>
        <p>vāḻcci, vāḻtalai yuṇarttuṅ kāl taṟkiḻamaiyumām.</p>
        <p>aṉṉapiṟavu meṉṟatu</p>
        <lg xml:id="TolC080-Nacc-cit33">
          <l>eṭcāntu</l>
        </lg>
        <lg xml:id="TolC080-Nacc-cit34">
          <l>kōṭṭu nūṟu</l>
        </lg>
        <p>ivai muḻutun tirintaṉa</p>
        <lg xml:id="TolC080-Nacc-cit35">
          <l>cāttaṉa toppu</l>
        </lg>
        <lg xml:id="TolC080-Nacc-cit36">
          <l>tokaiyatu viri</l>
        </lg>
        <lg xml:id="TolC080-Nacc-cit37">
          <l>poruḷatu kēṭu,</l>
        </lg>
        <lg xml:id="TolC080-Nacc-cit38">
          <l>collatu poruḷ,</l>
        </lg>
        <p>ivai ciṟitu tirintaṉa <num xml:lang="en">(19)</num></p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Teyvaccilaiyār</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">1929, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZU1k0My.TVA_BOK_0007188/page/n71/mode/1up">64</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZU1k0My.TVA_BOK_0007188/page/n72/mode/1up">65</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZU1k0My.TVA_BOK_0007188/page/n73/mode/1up">66</ref>.</p>
      <p>itu āṟām vēṟṟumaip poruḷ vēṟupāṭuṇarttutal nutaliṟṟu.</p>
      <p>i-ḷ:― iyaṟkai mutalāka vāḻcci yīṟāka eṇṇappaṭṭa kiḻamaiyiṉum, tirintu vēṟupaṭūum piṟavaṟṟiṉum, attaṉmaiyavāki mēṟcollappaṭṭa itaṉatu itu eṉum poruṭ ṭōṉṟum collellām āṟām vēṟṟumaip pālaṉa. e―ṟu.</p>
      <p>mēlaiccūttirattāṉ, uṭaiyāṉum uṭaipporuḷumākiya kiḻamai eṭuttōtiṉār iccūttirattāṉ ataṉiṉ vēṟupaṭṭu varuvaṉa eṭuttōtiṉār eṉṟu koḷka. iyaṟkai eṉpatu iyalpākiya kiḻamai. aḵtāvatu poruṭku iyalpākiya paṇpu. nilattatu vali. nīratu taṇmai. tīyatu vemmai eṉa varum. uṭaimai eṉpatu uṭaipporuḷiṉ pākupāṭu uṇara nillātu potumai uṇara niṟpatu. appotu kiḻamaiyiṉum varum eṉṟavāṟu.</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Tey-cit1">
        <l>cāttaṉatu uṭaimai</l>
      </lg>
      <p>eṉavarum.</p>
      cāttaṉatu kuḻai
      <p>eṉṟataṉōṭu itaṉiṭai vēṟṟumai eṉṉai yeṉiṉ,</p>
       <lg xml:id="TolC080-Tey-cit2">
        <l>cāttaṉatuṭaimai kuḻai</l>
      </lg>
      <p>eṉavum vantu, kuṟippu viṉaipporuḷoṭu muṭitaliṉ vēṟōtappaṭṭatu. viṉaikkuṟippu ōtukiṉṟavaḻi, atuc col vēṟṟumai yuṭaimai yāṉum<note place="foot">viṉaiyiyal―16</note> eṉṟu ōtiṉār ākaliṉ, īṇṭukkuḻai eṉa niṟṟalēyaṉṟik kuḻaiyai yuṭaiyaṉ eṉavum varutaliṉ īṇṭu vēṟupaṭuttu ōtalvēṇṭumeṉṟu uṇarka. muṟaimai eṉpatu uṭaiyāṉum uṭaipporuḷumaṉṟi, muṟaimaiyākiya kiḻamaiyāṉ varuvatu.</p>
       <lg xml:id="TolC080-Tey-cit3">
        <l>āviṉatu kaṉṟu, </l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Tey-cit4">
        <l>maṟiyatu tāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <p>kiḻamai eṉpatu urimai. aḵtāvatu ivaṟku ivaḷ uriyaḷ eṉṉum poruḷpaṭa varuvatu. muṟaimaiyai cāravaittataṉāl kiḻattiyareṉṟu koḷḷappaṭum. aracaṉatu urimai. ceyaṟkaiyāvatu, ceyaṟkaiyāṉ varuvatu.</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Tey-cit5">
        <l>cāttaṉatu kalvi,</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Tey-cit6">
        <l>cāttaṉatu kōlam.</l>
      </lg>
      <p>mutumai eṉpatu pariṇāmam kuṟittu niṟkum.</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Tey-cit7">
        <l>cāttaṉatu mutumai. </l>
      </lg>
      <p>vantatu koṇṭu vārātatu muṭittal<note place="foot">taṉṉiṉamuṭittal. iraṇṭavatēṭu.</note> eṉpataṉāl, iḷamaiyuṅ koḷka.</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Tey-cit8">
        <l>cāttaṉatu iḷamai.</l>
      </lg>
      <p>viṉaiyeṉpatu toḻil uṇara varuvatu.</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Tey-cit9">
        <l>cāttaṉatu varavu.</l>
      </lg>
      <p>karuvi eṉpatu uṭaimai kuṟiyātu itaṟkitu karuvi yeṉṉum poruḷpaṭa varuvatu.</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Tey-cit10">
        <l>yāṉaiyatu tōṭṭi,</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Tey-cit11">
        <l>vaṉaikalattatu tikiri.</l>
      </lg>
      <p>tuṇai yeṉpatu naṭpiṉ mēlvarum.</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Tey-cit12">
        <l>cāttaṉatu tuṇai itu.</l>
      </lg>
      <p>vantatu koṇṭu vārātatu muṭittal eṉpataṉāl pakaiyum koḷka.</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Tey-cit13">
        <l>cāttaṉatu pakai.</l>
      </lg>
      <p>māṟupāṭum iṉam ākumō eṉiṉ, māṟupāṭum apporuḷ kuṟittaliṉ iṉamām. kalam eṉpatu(?)</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Tey-cit14">
        <l>pālatukalam,</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Tey-cit15">
        <l>nilattatu vilaikkalam.</l>
      </lg>
      <p>mutaleṉpatu ciṉaiyōṭu aṭuttu mutaluṇara varuvatu.</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Tey-cit16">
        <l>koṭiyatu mutal.</l>
      </lg>
      <p>oruvaḻiyuṟuppu eṉpatu mutaloṭu ciṉaiyaṭuttu varuvatu.</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Tey-cit17">
        <l>caṇpakattatu kōṭu.</l>
      </lg>
      <p>kuḻāmeṉpatu palaporuṭṭokuti.</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Tey-cit18">
        <l>paṭaiyatu kuḻām,</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Tey-cit19">
        <l>nellatu kuppai.</l>
      </lg>
      <p>terintu moḻicceytiyāvatu terinta moḻiyiṉatu ceyal kūṟal.</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Tey-cit20">
        <l>pāṭṭatu karuttu,</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Tey-cit21">
        <l>pāṭṭatu poruḷ.</l>
      </lg>
      <p>nilai eṉpatu avaravar niṉṟa nilaimai kuṟittu varuvatu.</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Tey-cit22">
        <l>cāttaṉatu ilvāḻkkai,</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Tey-cit23">
        <l>cāttaṉatu tavam.</l>
      </lg>
      <p>vāḻcci’ eṉpatu iṭam paṟṟivarum.</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Tey-cit24">
        <l>yāṉaiyatu kāṭu,</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Tey-cit25">
        <l>kāṭṭatu yāṉai.</l>
      </lg>
      <p>tirintu vēṟu paṭuvaṉa,</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Tey-cit26">
        <l>eṇṇatu cāntu,</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Tey-cit27">
        <l>kōṭṭatu nūṟu.</l>
      </lg>
      <p>kūṟiya maruṅkiṟṟōṉṟuvaṉa,</p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Tey-cit28">
        <l>cāttaṉatu tōppu,</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Tey-cit29">
        <l>poruḷatu kēṭu, </l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Tey-cit30">
        <l>āviṉatu pāl,</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC080-Tey-cit31">
        <l>karumpiṉatu cāṟu</l>
      </lg>
      <p>eṉa innikaraṉa vellām koḷka. iṉṉuṅ kūṟiya maruṅkiṟṟōṉṟuṅ kiḷavi eṉpataṉāl, urupiṉ poruḷpaṭavarum uṭaiya veṉṉuñ colluṅ koḷka.	[18]
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
